  "texts": [
    "The goal of the TLP framework to enable quick and efficient decision making in the maintenance operation by assisting engineers, technicians, operators, and maintainers.",
    "There are many possible use-cases for such a framework across several industries.",
    "To demonstrate the potential applications of the proposed framework, we identify two scenarios in which it can be used to improve the maintenance operation of aircraft.",
    "There are a limited number of publicly available datasets with technical text.",
    "We use the Aviation Maintenance dataset that is originally from University of North Dakota's Aviation Program, made available by researchers (Akhbardeh et al., 2020a) on the open-source web-interface called Maintnet."
  ],
